{{etyl|enm}} ''[[disese#Middle English|disese]]'' from {{etyl|xno}} ''[[desese#Anglo-Norman|desese, disaise]]'' from {{etyl|fro}} {{term|desaise|lang=fro}} ({{prefix|dis|ease}}). Displaced native {{enm}} ''[[adle#Middle English|adle, audle]]'' "disease" (from {{ang}} ''[[adl#Old English|ādl]]'' "disease, sickness"), {{enm}} ''[[cothe#Middle English|cothe, coathe]]'' "disease" (from {{ang}} ''[[coþu#Old English|coþu]]'' "disease").

